Packages 
Package Description
Entities
Largest part of data, because the game mainly relies on the player, monsters, projectiles
Entities.LivingBeings
Sub package containing all the Living beings (Player and Monsters) data
Entities.LivingBeings.Monsters
Sub package containing all the monsters (Ranged and Melee) data
Entities.LivingBeings.Monsters.Melee
Sub package containing all the Melee monsters (Knight and KnightBoss) data
Entities.LivingBeings.Monsters.Ranged
Sub package containing all the Melee monsters (Bowman and BowmanBoss) data
Entities.Projectiles
Sub package containing all the projectiles data
HUD
In game visual elements such as healthbars, the end screen and the pause menu
HUD.HealthBars
Sub package containing all the healthbar renderers
Listeners
All the listeners of the game
Main
Main class and miscellaneous static use classes
Managers
Managers for data or user interface
Renderers
All the renderers for the entities and one for the font
